It's your meeting.

735
00:31:53.178 --> 00:31:55.128
(chuckles)

736
00:31:56.915 --> 00:32:00.750
Eight years ago. I was. um.
pregnant for the first time.

737
00:32:00.785 --> 00:32:04.338
And Randall was vying
for partner at his firm.

738
00:32:04.373 --> 00:32:07.457
We'd just bought this house
on faith.

739
